data.description: This hard to find 4 bedroom 2 bath home is located on a corner lot in a highly sought out neighborhood. You are literally minutes from shopping, dining, parks and Ft. Huachuca. Original owner since the home was built in 1976 and you can see the pride of ownership throughout. Separate dining room, large laundry room, fireplace, and two separate family rooms. New paint in the interior, new windows, new doors, and new plumbing. The expansive backyard has two sheds and endless possibilities!  Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary property your own!
